  2        KAVYA
  3        ANUSHKA
  4        KIRAN
  5        SUBBARAO



SQL>select * from PROJECTS;


  PID           PNAME                      EMPID
--------     -------------------          --------
  101        SENTIMENT ANALYSIS              3
  102        ONLINE VOTING SYSTEM            
  103        MOBILE APP DEVELOPMENT          2
  104        EMPLOYEE PAYROLL                1
  105        BANK ACCOUNT SYSTEM            




2.Write a query to display all projects and their assigned employees, if any. 
  Including unassigned projects.
ANS:
SQL> SELECT*FROM EMPLOYEES11 E RIGHT OUTER JOIN PROJECTS P ON E.EMPID=P.EMPID;

     EMPID ENAME             PID PNAME                               EMPID
---------- ---------- ---------- ------------------------------ ----------
         3 ANUSHKA           101 SENTIMENT ANALYSIS                  3
                             102 ONLINE VOTING SYSTEM
         2 KAVYA             103 MOBILE APP DEVELOPMENT              2
         1 SURYA             104 EMPLOYEE PAYROLL                    1
                             105 BANK ACCOUNT SYSTEM



3.Write a query to display all employees and all projects.If an employee is not assigned to any     project or a project is not assigned to any employee, display all details

ANS:

SELECT * FROM EMPLOYEES11 E1 LEFT JOIN PROJECTS P1 ON P1.EMPID=E1.EMPID; 

    EMPID ENAME             PID PNAME                               EMPID
---------- ---------- ---------- ------------------------------ ----------
         3 ANUSHKA           101 SENTIMENT ANALYSIS                  3
         2 KAVYA             103 MOBILE APP DEVELOPMENT              2
         1 SURYA             104 EMPLOYEE PAYROLL                    1
         4 KIRAN
         5 SUBBARAO


4.Write a query to display all employees and the projects they are working on, if any.
  Including employees not assigned to any project.

ANS:
SQL> SELECT*FROM EMPLOYEES11 E1 LEFT JOIN PROJECTS P ON E1.EMPID=P.EMPID;

     EMPID ENAME             PID PNAME                               EMPID
---------- ---------- ---------- ------------------------------ ----------
         3 ANUSHKA           101 SENTIMENT ANALYSIS                  3
         2 KAVYA             103 MOBILE APP DEVELOPMENT              2
         1 SURYA             104 EMPLOYEE PAYROLL                    1
         4 KIRAN
         5 SUBBARAO




