6.Write a query to display customers who have not placed any orders.

ANS:
 SQL> SELECT CUSTOMRNAME FROM CUSTOMERS C1 LEFT JOIN ORDERS O1 ON C1.CUSTOMERID=O1.CUSTOMERID WHERE O1.CUSTOMERID IS NULL;

CUSTOMRNAM
----------
GOWTHAM
KIRAN



7.Write a query to display all customers along with their order details, 
  including those customers who have not placed any orders.

ANS:
  SQL> SELECT*FROM CUSTOMERS C1 LEFT JOIN ORDERS O1 ON C1.CUSTOMERID=O1.CUSTOMERID;

CUSTOMERID CUSTOMRNAM    ORDERID CUSTOMERID ORDERDATE  TOTAMOUNT
